text: LY-2452473 (TT-701) is a drug which acts as a selective androgen receptor modulator (SARM). It has been investigated for the treatment of erectile dysfunction and symptoms associated with benign prostate hyperplasia. ==See also== * Enobosarm * JNJ-28330835 * Ligandrol == References == Category:Selective androgen receptor modulators
title: LY-2452473
